data.description: Spacious and affordable best describes this home and located just minutes from Greers Ferry Lake.  Features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 living areas, large master suite & bath, & separate laundry room & pantry.  Also includes a detached garage, separate storage building, wood deck and the master suite has a separate bath, walk-in closet, and private patio area all sitting on 1 acre.   If you are needing extra space inside and outside, this is the property for you!   Also handicap accessible.  Look at this home today! 2023-10-30
